Put the salt in the right hand drawer underneath the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn and go to the end of the counter on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the second salt and pepper shaker from the cabinet on your left.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter or the right side of the stove.
Put the salt and pepper shaker in the drawer on the right side of the counter under the coffee maker.
